name: Caltron 6 in 1
overview:
Six of the newest video games in one cartridge. You get all 6 of the newest games for the price of one. Saves you space and convinience to operate.

Cosmos Cop: Action packed space war game. High skill neccesary.
Magic Carpet 1001: To catch the treasure of the Magic Lamp, then you win the game. Has 4 levels.
Balloon Monster: To exhange Time with Space. Hit the bubbles at its highest point. 50 levels.
Adam and Eve: To kill all snakes and catch all apples in order to win. 40 levels.
Porter: Testing your IQ. Move all boxes to where the stars are. Has 25 levels.
Bookyman: Clean the streets and keep it clean while trying to keep alive. 8 levels.
